The evidence with the title 'A Thousand Small Sanities ' says Jan 30, 2012  ... This story is fairly well known , if not well understood. Less well known is a crucial piece of the . New York narrative: in addition to reducing crime,. New York has also managed to reduce the use of incarceration . From 1999 to 2009, the incidence of violent crime declined by 30 percent in New York State . 
